al line to reach the new location of the furnace and make all necessary electrical connections · Seal all new supply and return duct connections with Mastic and Hard-Cast Foil-Grip Tape in order to eliminate the excess leakage of air into the crawlspace · Install Insulation over the supply and return plenums in the crawlspace

